posts.body:
Coming Soon: Qamaria Yemeni Coffee Featured in Rich Woman Magazine!


Qamaria Yemeni Coffee is opening soon in University City — and we’re already making headlines!

We’re honored to be featured in Rich Woman Magazine as Charlotte’s next late-night coffee retreat. Expect authentic Yemeni flavors, warm hospitality, spiced brews, and a cozy atmosphere perfect for studying, relaxing, or gathering with friends.

“Officially Announced 🎉: Qamaria Yemeni Coffee is coming soon to University City, Charlotte! Experience bold flavors, cozy late-night vibes, and authentic Yemeni culture in every cup. Click to read the full press release!”

reviews_data.review_text:
Visited on opening day- expecting it to be packed, but to my surprise there were still a few tables open.  The ambiance, however, was great. The decor had intricate details that truly reflected Yemen and with the arabic music playing in the background, it truly felt like you were transported there.

We tried the pistachio latte, Qamaria latte, pistachio milk cake, kunafe cup, and bee bites. I really liked the Qamaria latte- perfectly balanced with just the right touch of cardamom. My husband usually doesn’t like sweets, but he finished the entire slice of bee bite- which is a big deal.. lol. The pistachio milk cake was okayish, and the kunafe cup wasn’t as good as I expected. The menu overall felt a little limited, I wish they had included some savory options. But since it was their very first day, I believe they kept things simple for the launch and may expand it later.

Even though it didn’t fully match my expectations, I’d still say it was definitely worth the visit.

I was able to go on opening day. It’s such a beautiful place from the flooring to the ceiling. I was in awe of the decor. The staff was friendly and my order came out in a timely manner. I was able to enjoy my coffee and cake inside the coffee shop. It was a nice experience. The pistachio latte was delicious and the pistachio cake was delicious as well.

I was able to park in the parking garage with ease. I will be back I love how spacious it is inside. I look forward to exploring more on their menu.

Really great staff! Owner is so sweet and genuinely cares about her customers. The milk cakes and pastries are delicious. The iced pistachio latte was also really good. The best part is location and ambiance. The decoration is top tier and makes me feel like I could sit here for hours.
Nice place for some good Middle Eastern Beverages
I absolutely recommend Qamaria! The staff is incredibly warm and welcoming. I had the iced pistachio latte and honeycomb bites, which were absolutely delicious.

Qamaria Yemeni Coffee isn’t just another cafe it’s a full on experience. From the moment you walk in, the warm hospitality and rich aroma of spices set the tone for something special. If you’re tired of the same old coffee chains, this place is a breath of fresh air.
I ordered the Yemeni adeni tea and it was incredible beautifully balanced with spices like cardamom. just sweet enough without being overpowering. It’s smooth, fragrant, and unlike anything you’ll find at a typical coffee shop. It’s the kind of drink you sip slowly because you don’t want it to end.
The appetizers wow specially the bint alsahn (Yemeni honey butter bread) is delicious, fresh, and clearly made with care. Perfectly flaky, warm, and paired so well with the adni tea and goes with any other hot drinks.
The space itself is clean, welcoming, and full of cultural touches that make it feel authentic yet comfortable. Staff were kind, knowledgeable, and happy to show u and serve u. if you’re unfamiliar with Yemeni coffee traditions.
Highly recommend Qamaria for anyone looking to expand their coffee horizons. Whether you’re a casual coffee drinker, tea drinker or a full on enthusiast, this place is worth the trip.
A cozy hidden gem where great coffee meets’s great vibes and cool people.
My experience has been nothing short than amazing! Love, Love, LOVE the food here as well as enjoy the people and the atmosphere. I can’t wait to come back.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much  for the kind words ! Thrilled to hear that you loved the food , atmosphere and our lovely team . It means the world that your experience has been amazing , and we truly can't wait to welcome you back again soon !

reviews_data.review_text: Coffee is amazing, the pastries are delicious, and plenty of bright comfortable space where to sit and relax or work! I'll definitely be back.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much Lorenzo ! We're  so happy you enjoyed the coffee , pastries and the space . Can't wait to welcome you back for another visit soon !

reviews_data.review_text: The sheeba is delicious. The staff are lovely. Amazing ambiance. Great food!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much Candice ! We're so glad you enjoyed the Sheba  and the ambiance . Can't wait to welcome you back soon !

reviews_data.review_text: Great location. Great people!. Great service Great pastries!. Great desserts!. Great beverage. Great atmosphere.

reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you , Ahmad ! We're so glad you enjoyed the atmosphere , service , and pasties . We truly appreciate your support and look forward to seeing you  again soon !

reviews_data.review_text: The place is absolutely beautiful and the food and drinks were perfect!! The customer service was great!!! I will definitely be back! I highly recommend this place for any occasion. It was a 10/10
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much ! We're glad you enjoyed everything and can wait to see you again  soon .

reviews_data.review_text:
Was really excited to pop in before the grand opening on Friday Aug 22, 2025 and sample the Mango Dragonfruit and my husband had the Strawberry Dragonfruit!

Cant wait for opening because this was so refreshing and real fruit!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for stopping by to try our refreshers ! We can't wait to see you again at our soft opening 🎉

reviews_data.review_text: I got the strawberry lemonade refresher and it was delicious, not too sweet and so refreshing. The customer service was amazing!
reviews_data.owner_answer: We're so glad you loved the strawberry lemonade refresher and our service . We look forward to seeing you again .
